---
title: Smokey Beef Rissoles & Parmesan Wedges with Cucumber Slaw & Lemon Yoghurt
description: What happens when you mix beef mince, garlic, breadcrumbs, egg and our crowd favourite Berbere seasoning? You get these
juicy and flavour-packed rissoles! Add crunch with a refreshing slaw and crispy Parmesan on golden wedges for a little slice of heaven.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

*Keep an eye out... Due to sourcing challenges over the Christmas period, some of the fresh ingredients you receive may be slightly different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
